50 50 translate

1 setlinecap

/S 44 def
S dup scale
1 S div setlinewidth
/Pi 3.1415926536 def

gsave
0.7 setgray
-90 10 90 { /i exch def
i cos i sin moveto
i cos neg i sin lineto
} for
stroke
grestore

/N 9 def
/x 0 def
/dx //Pi 2 div N div def
/M 16 def

gsave
0.7 setgray
newpath
N {
  /x dx x add def
  /X x 180 mul //Pi div def
  X cos X sin moveto
  1 X sin lineto
} repeat
stroke
grestore

/x 0 def
/dx //Pi -2 div N div def

gsave
0.7 setgray
newpath
N {
  /x dx x add def
  /X x 180 mul //Pi div def
  X cos X sin moveto
  1 X sin lineto
} repeat
stroke
grestore

